metadata.dc:description: It presents three cases of Mullerian anomalies with septate uterus and cervical duplication and longitudinal vaginal septum. There are a few previous cases reported. The cases are discussed and the literature is revised.
metadata.dc:title: Utero septado con duplicación cervical y tabique vaginal: una malformación rara.
[Septate uterus with cervical duplication and vaginal partition: a rare malformation].
